FAN-MADE PROJECT NOTICE:
This is an unofficial, fan-made, non-profit project created for entertainment
and educational purposes only. This system is NOT affiliated with, endorsed by,
or connected to Nintendo, Intelligent Systems, or any official products.

TRADEMARK ACKNOWLEDGMENT:
This project is inspired by mechanics from tactical strategy games. All original
game concepts, mechanics, and intellectual property belong to their respective
copyright holders. This project makes no claim to any official content.

ORIGINAL SOURCE ATTRIBUTION:
This system is based on the tabletop Fire Emblem RPG adaptation created by Dylan B., as
documented in the community-created manual available at:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1-XWn9U0fddjyDkfu3tLEZECS7CrY75_I/view

The game mechanics and system design are derived from Dylan B.'@ + "'" + @'s work, adapted
for use with Foundry Virtual Tabletop.

